1. *Droga* se nalazi u blizini škole. (The drug is located near the school.)
2. Ona je uzele *drogu*. (She took the drug.)
3. On je otkrio da je ovisnik o *drogi*. (He discovered he was addicted to the drug.)
4. Oni su uhvaćeni sa *drogom*. (They were caught with the drug.)
5. Ne treba da se bavite *drogom*. (You should not be involved with drugs.)
6. *Droga* se koriste za liječenje. (Drugs are used for treatment.)